<div class="main-content-overflow">
  <div class="questionnaire levels">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <h2 class="ipt-title-question">{{question.name}}</h2>
        <p>{{{question.content}}}</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <form class="project-levels">
          <div class="level-container row">
            <div class="col-sm-1">
              <input type="radio" name="questionnaire-level" value="1">
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8 level-description">
              <h3>Quick Assessment</h3>
              <p class="radio-text ipt-levels">The quick assessment will help you getting a first, high-level assessment of your project.</p>
              <p class="radio-text mm-levels">The quick assessment will help you getting a first, high-level assessment of your organization.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2 level-timeframe">
              <p class="ipt-levels">15-30 mins</p>
              <p class="mm-levels">5 mins</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="level-container row">
            <div class="col-sm-1">
              <input type="radio" name="questionnaire-level" value="2">
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8 level-description">
              <h3>Standard Assessment</h3>
              <p class="radio-text ipt-levels">The standard assessment will provide you with a level that will be sufficient for many project managers as a starting point, e.g. for a vendor RFI/RFP (Request of information/Proposal)</p>
              <p class="radio-text mm-levels">The standard assessment will provide you with an enhanced understanding of your organizationâ€™s current status</p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2 level-timeframe">
              <p class="ipt-levels">60-120 mins</p>
              <p class="mm-levels">15 mins</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="level-container row">
            <div class="col-sm-1">
              {{#if detailedEnabled}}
                <input type="radio" name="questionnaire-level" value="3">
              {{/if}}
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-8 level-description">
              <h3>Detailed Assessment</h3>
              <p class="radio-text ipt-levels">The detailed assessment is in-depth, covering additional technical questions, e.g. as a prerequisite for a detailed solution design. <u>This level is only available to IIC memebers and their customers.</u></p>
              <p class="radio-text mm-levels">The detailed assessment will walk you through the full detail included in the IIoT Maturity Model. <u>This level is only available to IIC memebers and their customers.</u></p>
            </div>
            <div class="col-sm-2 level-timeframe">
              <p class="ipt-levels">120-180 mins</p>
              <p class="mm-levels">25 mins</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12 spider-container">
        <svg class="spider" width="800" height="700"></svg>
        <div class='test'></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="questionnaire question buttons-fixed">
  <div class="buttons row">
    <div class="col-sm-4">
      <button class="back levels-back question-back">back</button>
    </div>
    <div class="col-sm-4 col-sm-push-4">
      <button class="next levels-next question-next">NEXT</button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>